channel.title: Reached the end of file while parsing. What it mean and how fix
channel.description:
I got this error in my client comiler:
[code]Galkon's Compiler By Galkon
Class23.java:44: reached end of file while parsing }→ ^ 1 error Compile successful! Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Anyone know what it means, and how to fix it? Help is appreciated.
